item.title: Can torque to yield bolts be reused
item.description: How many times can torque-to-yield bolts be used? * Never reuse a torque-to-yield bolt. Because the bolts are designed to stretch once, stretching them a second time may stretch them beyond their yield point causing the bolt to break. They are one-time use bolts, so throw the old bolts away and buy new ones. Can you use torque-to-yield bolts twice? However, because the tightening procedure does permanently stretch the bolt, there is some risk of breakage if the bolt is reused.

item.title: Could O.J. Simpson Be Khloe Kardashians Father?
item.description: The rumor mill is going crazy with allegations that O.J. Simpson is claiming to be the biological father of Khloe Kardashian—even going to the length of putting her in his will. In this bizarre report, The National Enquirer suggests that a source confirmed O.J.’s belief that Khloe was birthed through an affair with Kris Jenner while she was still married to her now-deceased husband Robert Kardashian. As far as his will—which is said to be in the millions and expected to grow—O.

item.title: Queen Key Posts Video Of 600 Breezy Giving Her Head (NSFW)
item.description: Seeing that Queen Key‘s last two projects are titled Eat My Pussy and Eat My Pussy Again, it’s probably safe to say the Chicago-bred rapper loves oral sex. Now, there’s actual footage of Key receiving cunnilingus by “Thuggin” rapper 600 Breezy as she took to Twitter to expose Breezy and his kitty-eating skills (or lack thereof) after an apparent breakup. She’s also getting ready to release a single titled “Make Me Cum.” AD LOADING...

item.title: Who is Blake Griffins Ex-Fiance Brynn Cameron? Her Kids, Age
item.description: Who is Brynn Cameron? Brynn Cameron is one of those ladies well-known for being the ex-fiancee of a celebrity star. She is also the former basketball star, better known as Blake Griffin’s ex-fiance, an NBA star. Even though the relationship is no longer, Brynn still is remembered in the spotlight. Brynn is an athlete in her own right. She was a professional basketball player in the past and a college player.

item.title: Woman Cracking Up in Chewbacca Mask Goes Viral
item.description: It’s the little things! Star Wars superfan Candace Payne treated herself to a Chewbacca mask for her birthday and couldn’t stop laughing when she tried it on. Luckily, she caught the hilarious moment on camera — and quickly became a viral star. “Hey, I’m really excited to share with you something I got,” Payne says at the beginning of her video — which already has more than 58 million views — as she claps with a huge smile on her face.

item.title: DJ Envy Linked To Multi-Million Dollar Real Estate Ponzi Scheme
item.description: Highlights DJ Envy, known for hosting The Breakfast Club, is facing backlash for his alleged involvement in a "ponzi scheme" related to a real estate venture. Investors who put money into the venture are claiming it was a scam and are expressing frustration at the lack of returns on their investments. DJ Envy has denied any involvement in the scheme, stating that he hosted seminars to educate his community about real estate and invested his own money in the project.

item.title: Help! Why Do My Leggings Roll Down?
item.description: The workday is behind you and you're ready to dedicate an hour to moving your body. Maybe you're Zooming in to a yoga class, or heading out the front door for a run around you local park. Either way, you get about 10 minutes into your workout and—bam—your leggings start shimmying down your torso and bunching uncomfortably on your legs. (Ugh! They have one job!) We've all been there, but Casey Ho—internet-renowned TikToker and founder of Blogilates—says there's an easy trick to predict if your bottoms are going to roll down and ruin your workout.

item.title: Jamie Lynn Spears Cries, Says Relationship With Sister Britney Is 'Complicated'
item.description: Jamie Lynn Spears became overcome with emotion while speaking about her relationship with her sister Britney Spears on Good Morning America. In a promo clip for the highly anticipated interview, the actress said she “loves” her sister but acknowledges that “things have gotten complicated.” Jamie Lynn Breaks Down While Talking About Her Relationship With Her Sister Britney Spears. The Sweet Magnolias star sat down with ABC News journalist Juju Chang a week before the release of her tell-all memoir.

item.title: Jason Robins' Net Worth How DraftKings CEO Became a Billionaire
item.description: Jason Robins is the co-founder and CEO of DraftKings — how much is he worth in 2022? Plus, how much is his company worth today? We have all the details. When it comes to sports betting, there is no denying that DraftKings is dominating the field. item.title: Marvel, And The Financial Fallout Of The Jonathan Majors Verdict
item.description: Highlights Actor Jonathan Majors, known for his roles in Lovecraft Country and Ant-Man and The Wasp: Quantumania , has been found guilty on charges of reckless assault and harassment in relation to a domestic incident involving his former girlfriend, Grace Jabbari. Majors' guilty verdict has resulted in swift action from Marvel Studios, who have cut all ties with him and will no longer work with him on the upcoming project Avengers: The Kang Dynasty .

item.title: Miley Cyrus Still Has Vegemite Tattoo After Liam Hemsworth Split: Photo
item.description: Miley Cyrus has made yet another tattoo-related change to her life. The “Wrecking Ball” singer took to Instagram on Monday, October 21, to share that she paid a visit to a tattoo parlor and added a new design to her ever-growing array of ink. The 26-year-old posted an update via the photo-sharing app to joke about a “tat shop touch up,” as she shared a series of photos of herself applying lipstick in a tattoo shop.

item.title: Robin Meade
item.description: Robin Meade- Biography Robin Meade is a well-known co-host and anchors the HLN morning show The Morning Express. Similarly, Robin Meade has dabbled in the world of music. What is the Net Worth of Robin Meade? Salary, Earnings According to numerous web sources, Robin’s annual salary is reported to be around $3 million. Her primary source of income is her work as a news anchor and host. Aside from that, she has profited from the sale of her book and, to a lesser extent, her music.

item.title: The Fanciest, Most Expensive Bread In The World
item.description: Quick LinksTortilla Focaccia Rugbrod Miche Harrods Roquefort and Almond Sourdough Bread The Shepherd Loaf The Royal Bloomer The Gold Leaf Bread The most exclusive bakers are zealously guarding their trade secrets, so they probably won't spill their cherished secrets. It is not a surprise that the cost of these baked goods rises, and they are considered some of the best masterpieces in the world, and they adore bread.

item.title: 'Dancing With the Stars' Pros That Have Left and Why
item.description: Dancing With the Stars has found plenty of success since its debut in 2005. Over the years, the ABC dancing competition has launched the careers of many new pros and has said goodbye to a few OGs along the way. Julianne Hough, who competed from seasons 4 to season 8, announced in 2009 that she was leaving to pursue other interests. Hough went on to kickstart her career as an actress — but didn’t rule out a DWTS comeback.

item.title: Usher To Receive Lifetime Achievement Award At 2024 BET Awards
item.description: Usher is still at thetop of his game, as BET has announced him as their 2024 Lifetime Achievement Award recipient. The coveted honor celebrates “industry pioneers who have powerfully shifted culture and the entertainment industry.” Previous recipients include Whitney Houston, Prince, Queen Latifah, Anita Baker, Mary J. Blige, Samuel Jackson, Lionel Richie, andNew Edition. “The relationship between BET and Usher spans decades, from his multiple appearances on 106 & Park, to most recently winning the Entertainer of the Year trophy at the 55th NAACP Image Awards,” said Connie Orlando, BET EVP, Specials, Music Programming & Music Strategy, in a statement.

While it’s been more than 30 years since The Addams Family was first released in 1991, the film has endured as one of the most popular Halloween flicks and even spawned several spinoffs and sequels. item.title: Uhuru Park To Be Handed Back To Nairobi County Government On Thursday
item.description: Uhuru Park will be officially handed back to the Nairobi County government on Thursday morning, according to Defence Cabinet Secretary Aden Duale. Speaking in Parliament on Wednesday, Duale stated that the majority of renovation work at the park is complete, with only minor tasks remaining for Central Park. “I’m handing over Uhuru Park to Nairobi County Gov’t tomorrow morning at 9am, running parks is not our core mandate,” said Duale.
